The paper discusses a proposal for all-optical machine learning using diffractive deep neural networks, which involves pattern classification using a strictly linear optical setup. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and information theory (cs.IT), as well as optical hardware (cs.OH) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI).
